# Smart Tracker & Timeline System - Feasibility & Plan

This document outlines the feasibility and implementation strategy for adding an intelligent document tracker and a WhatsApp-style activity timeline to FamilySphere.

## Feasibility Analysis
The proposed system is **highly feasible** with your current stack (Node.js, MongoDB Atlas, Flutter, Cloudinary).

### Why it works:
- **Scalable Backend**: MongoDB Atlas is perfect for storing unstructured metadata extracted via OCR.
- **Efficient UI**: Flutter's Clean Architecture allows us to plug in the timeline and tracker as independent features.
- **Activity Logging**: Your existing `FamilyActivity` model provides a solid foundation for the notification/timeline feed.

## Strategic Approach

### 1. The "Peak Performance" Pipeline
To achieve peak performance, especially on a platform like Render, we must avoid blocking the main backend thread.

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Upload Doc] --> B[Store in Cloudinary]
    B --> C[Background Worker]
    C --> D[OCR Extraction]
    D --> E[AI Classification]
    E --> F[Update MongoDB & Create Event]
    F --> G[Push Notification]
```

> [!TIP]
> **Performance Optimization**: Use a separate microservice or a background queue (like BullMQ with Redis) for OCR and AI processing. This ensures the user isn't waiting for the upload to "complete" while AI runs.

### 2. Intelligent Document Engine
Instead of folder-based logic, we rely on **Metadata Extraction**.

- **Phase 1 (Basic)**: Keyword-based detection using Regex on extracted OCR text.
- **Phase 2 (Advanced)**: Send the top 1000 characters of OCR text to an LLM (Claude/GPT) to return a structured JSON of the document type, dates, and amounts.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Backend (Node.js)

#### [MODIFY] [Document.ts](file:///d:/FamilySphere/backend/src/models/Document.ts)
Update schema to include `extractedMetadata`, `reminderEnabled`, and `reminderSettings`.

#### [NEW] [ocrService.ts](file:///d:/FamilySphere/backend/src/services/ocrService.ts)
A service to handle PDF/Image text extraction using Google Vision AI or AWS Textract.

#### [NEW] [scheduler.ts](file:///d:/FamilySphere/backend/src/services/scheduler.ts)
A daily cron job (node-cron) to check for upcoming deadlines and trigger `FamilyActivity` events + `FCM` notifications.

### [Component] Mobile (Flutter)

#### [NEW] [timeline_screen.dart](file:///d:/FamilySphere/mobile/familysphere_app/lib/features/home/presentation/screens/timeline_screen.dart)
A WhatsApp-style feed using `ListView.builder` with `sticky_headers` for date grouping.

#### [MODIFY] [document_upload_provider.dart](file:///d:/FamilySphere/mobile/familysphere_app/lib/features/documents/presentation/providers/document_upload_provider.dart)
Update to handle the "Smart Detection" preview before final save.

